          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "Also, last time we checked, Dodge D100s weren’t super-hot theft items. Sure, they’re probably fairly easy to hotwire, but they’re not exactly a 1970 Plymouth ‘Cuda. While the owner obviously loves the truck, this isn’t some ultra-valuable collectable everyone and their grandma’s dog dreams of owning, whether through legitimate means or not.",
