          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": " from this crime pandemic and you really have to ask why that is. There are plenty of theories with many in the media blaming everything on the covid lockdowns. While those probably didn’t help, there’s also the problem of catch-and-release justice systems with judges giving out light sentences to car thieves. Others argue a general attitude of lawlessness is also to blame. Then there’s the chip shortage as well as other materials, making all cars of any age worth more.",
